Open your browser and search github.
Now open Github.com link and sign up using your collage gmail id.(23020...@silveroakuni.ac.in)
Now in browser search git and open git-scm.com link.
After that download git bash to your respective machine.
The Install the git. And chech the installition is complete or not using git --version type in your git bash.
Then open your github account and login using your gmail or username.
After Log in your present screen is Overview page. Go to the Repositories page and click on new button.
A new page is discover in your screen. Their give the name of repositorie.(Your Enrollnment Number)
Scroll down and check the checkbox of add a README file.
Then Click on Check Repository Button.
Congratulations! Now you create your first Repository  on github.
Now open you repositpory and click on Add file option and then click Create new file.
When new page is show on your screen the on file name box enter Assignment_1/ and press enter.
Now another box enter your fil name(git_step.txt) and write your all steps.
Then on this page press Commit changes button and again press Commit changes.
Then again click Add file and then Click on Upload files.
Now select your all file or pdfs. And Press commit chamges.
Thank You.
